'''Android 2.3 Gingerbread'''是[[谷歌|谷歌]]开发的[[Android|Android]]移动操作系统的第七个版本，于2010年12月发布。Gingerbread引入了对[[近场通信|近场通信]]（NFC）和[[對話啟動協定|對話啟動協定]]（SIP）的支持<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.cnet.com/news/whats-new-in-googles-android-2-3-gingerbread/|title = What's new in Google's Android 2.3 Gingerbread?|date = December 7, 2010|accessdate = September 3, 2015|website = CNET|publisher = |last = Graham|first = Flora|archive-date = 2018-08-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180811032308/https://www.cnet.com/news/whats-new-in-googles-android-2-3-gingerbread/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2010年12月发布的[[Nexus_S|Nexus S]]智能手机，是谷歌[[Nexus系列|Nexus系列]]中第一款运行Gingerbread的手机，也是该系列中第一款内置NFC功能的手机<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.engadget.com/2010/11/15/the-nexus-s-a-closer-look/|title = The Nexus S: a closer look|date = November 15, 2010|accessdate = September 3, 2015|website = Engadget|publisher = |last = Hollister|first = Sean|archive-date = 2019-04-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190422135922/https://www.engadget.com/2010/11/15/the-nexus-s-a-closer-look/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

截至2020年4月，谷歌发布的统计数据显示，在所有访问過[[Google_Play|Google Play]]的[[Android|Android]]设备中，有0.2%的设备依舊运行著Gingerbread<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://developer.android.com/about/dashboards/index.html|title=Distribution dashboard|website=Android Developers|accessdate=May 14, 2019|archive-date=2017-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501192418/https://developer.android.com/about/dashboards/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[Google|Google]]宣布，2021年9月27日後將不再支援2.3.7及更舊版的Android 手機上登入 [[Google|Google]]，同時代表[[Gmail|Gmail]]、[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Google_Maps|Google Maps]]等服務將受影響<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hktecmedia.com/237android-gmail/|title=舊款Android將不能用 Gmail、Google Maps、YouTube|website=hkTec|accessdate=Aug 4, 2021|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814095333/https://hktecmedia.com/237android-gmail/}}</ref>。

